tr_errorActionText: Nisy olana nitranga ka azonao averina sokafana ny pejy. Raha mbola tsy mety, dia avereno hatramin’ny voalohany mihitsy ny Organized. Hifafa daholo ny rakitra tsy mbola vita fampifanitsiana rehetra raha misafidy an’io ianao.
tr_appAboutDesc:
Natao mba hampiasain’ny fiangonan’ny Vavolombelon’i Jehovah ny Organized. Noforonina izy mba ho mora kokoa ny famitana ny andraikitra nankinina amin’ny tsirairay ao amin’ny fiangonana, sy mba handrindrana tsara ny anjara omena ny tsirairay.

Tsy sahirana intsony ianao manamboatra ny fandaharam-pivoriana andavanandro sy faran’ny herinandro, mandefa tatitra, ary mijery ny anjaranao amin’ny fivoriana. Azon’ny rehetra ao amin’ny fiangonana ampiasaina izy ity.

Manao ezaka izahay mba hanatsarana azy ity foana sy mba hampidirina zava-baovao fanampiny amin’ny hoavy. Afaka manampy anay amin’izany ianao, raha tianao. Azonao atao ny manohana anay amin’ny fanomezana izay foinao, na koa manampy anay fanamboarana ity programa ity, raha mahay manamboatra programa ianao.
tr_supportAppDesc: Maimaim-poana ny Organized, ary mahafaly ny manamboatra azy ity sy mizara azy ity ho anao. Mafana fo izahay manao an’izany na dia misy vola mila aloa aza amin’ny fikarakarana azy ity. Ankasitrahanay sy isaoranay ireo izay te hanohana anay amin’izany!
tr_supportAppOption1Desc: Ny fanomezana ataonao no ahafahanay manome ny Organized ho maimaim-poana mba ho ampiasain’ny fiangonana maro! Handoavana saran’ny serveur ampiasaina ireny fanomezana, sy mba hanamboarana zava-baovao.
tr_supportAppOption2Desc:
Tena ankasitrahanay ny fanampianao amin’ireto manaraka ireto:

  • React development
  • UI/UX Design
  • Fandikan-teny

Mifandraisa aminay raha afaka manampy anay amin’ireo ianao. Andao isika hiara-miasa mba hanatsarana ny Organized.

Azonao atao koa ny manome soso-kevitra ny hafa mba hampiasa Organized. Tena manampy be anay izay azonao atao mba hanohanana an’ity programa ity, amin’izay mba handray soa avy amin’izy ity ny rehetra.
tr_internalError: Nisy olana avy aty aminay. Andramo indray rehefa afaka kelikely.
tr_themeFollowOSDisable: Ajanona ny fampitoviana ho azy ny endrika isehon’ny fitaovana sy ny programa?
tr_themeFollowOSDisableDesc: Azonao ovana ao amin’ny pejy misy ny mombamomba anao indray izany avy eo, raha tianao handeha ho azy indray
tr_2FATokenInvalidExpired: Misy diso ny kaody na tsy azo ampiasaina intsony. Hamarino indray azafady.
tr_featureComingSoonDesc: Tsy mbola vonona aloha izao io. Mbola eo am-panamboarana an’ilay izy izahay. Kely sisa!
tr_pinRequired: Ampidiro ny kaody PIN raha te hijery na hanova fanazavana.
tr_changeAccessCodeDesc: Raha manahy ianao hoe mety misy mahita ny rakitra ampiasain’ny fiangonana, nefa tsy nahazo alalana, dia amin’izay ihany izahay no mampirisika ny hanovana an’ireo kaody miafina ampiasainareo. Tehirizo tsara sy omeo ireo mampiasa Organized rehetra ny kaody vaovao tokony omena azy aorian’izay.
tr_unsupportedBrowserErrorDesc: Programa tsy mety amin’ny programa Organized ity ampiasainao ity. Ataovy azo antoka hoe vita fanavaozana tsara izy ity aloha, sady tsy mampiasa navigation privée ianao. Azonao atao koa ny manandrana mampiasa programa hafa fijerena internet.
tr_noPersonsFoundDesc: Tsy misy olona hita ao amin’ny firaketana mifanaraka amin’ireo sivana ireo. Afaka misafidy sokajy na daty hafa koa ianao.
tr_wholeYearIsSelected: The 'Whole year' option is currently selected
tr_forceRefreshButtonTooltip: Force refresh the app to check for updates if they aren't showing up. No data will be cleared.
tr_noNotificationsDesc: Important notifications will be displayed here.
tr_userRoleChangedDesc: Your access in Organized has been changed recently. Log in to your account again for the changes to take effect.
